COMPUTE:
- Virtual Servers for VPC — Intel/AMD virtual machines in IBM Cloud VPC
- Bare Metal Servers — dedicated physical servers for high-performance workloads
- IBM Cloud Kubernetes Service — managed Kubernetes
- Red Hat OpenShift on IBM Cloud — managed OpenShift (IBM's preferred container platform)
